data.description: If privacy is what you are looking for, look no further. This turn key, 3br/2bath, 2537 sq.ft home has been beautifully updated, and is located on a quiet dead end road in the desirable Deer Park area. Plenty of room for RV and toy parking and/or pasture for your critters. Sit on the large deck or in the hot tub and watch all the wildlife the Deer Park area has to offer. A detached, 2 car garage/shop and additional outbuildings with lean-to's offer tons of covered parking, storage, or shelter for animals.
